Author: hibyelxsa
Text: You're right. I need to not beat myself up over this.

Author: BluntCakes_
Text: Hey hey hey, it’s alright. It’s alright. You only had oatmeal, soup, and a protein bar today and you need the vitamins and nutrients to survive. Please don’t beat yourself up over this, I know it’s hard, but you deserve to feel okay. It really isn’t that much food at all, anyone on the outside would yell at you “That’s it???” And I get it, it feels terrible. But you’re not a bad person because you ate and it won’t hurt you.
